Вакансія від 19 березня 2020
Sales Manager (personal protective equipment, LS)
IBC Nanotex
Гуртова торгівля, дистрибуція, імпорт, експорт;
менше 10 співробітників
Київ
Повна зайнятість.
Досвід роботи від 2 років.
Вища освіта.
Опис вакансії
Sales Manager — Personal protective equipment — LSKyiv, UkraineYour obligations:• Establishing and maintaining good and professional relationships with customers and business partners while providing high-level services• Recognizing customer needs, monitoring key customer activity, advising and creating appropriate business offers• Finding new customers and expanding your sales network• Proposing activities and strategies for improving and expanding business in the Ukrainian market• Preparing offers, invoices and other sales documentation• Monitoring and securing the collection of sales documentation• Maintaining adequate communication and coordination with other departments of the company in order to provide timely and quality customer service• Monthly and quarterly report• Monitoring of market trends and competition activitiesYour profile:• Minimum of 3 years work experience in sales in the same or similar positions / jobs (PPE)• Excellent computer skills, MS Office (Excel, Word)• Active and good knowledge of English• B category driver’s license, active driverAdvantages:• Knowledge of PPE safety equipment• Knowledge of the Ukrainian market• Evidence of completed training in sales techniques and skills, customer care, and negotiation skillsWe offer you:• Working for an international company• Incentive earnings• Excellent working conditions• Advancement in business• New experiences• A pleasant work atmosphereCandidates who submit a complete CV in English language with a photo will be contacted Please send your CV to: [відгукнутися]
